OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry end to
OL,6,Fthe day for most with some evening
OL,7,Fsunshine for many. Steadily becoming
OL,8,Fcloudier overnight with scattered
OL,9,Fshowers developing, these most likely
OL,10,Fin eastern counties. Mostly mild but
OL,11,Flocally turning chilly under if skies
OL,12,Fclear. Light winds.
OL,13,
OL,14,CWednesday:FA cloudy start for most
OL,15,Fwith the odd shower. Brightening up
OL,16,Ffor some by the afternoon but heavy
OL,17,Fslow-moving showers may develop in
OL,18,FCornwall and west Devon. Feeling
OL,19,Fsomewhat cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
