OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FScattered showers on Thursday and
OL,7,FFriday, mainly in the afternoons, but
OL,8,Fstaying dry for some. Longer periods
OL,9,Fof rain are possible on Saturday.
OL,10,FTurning warmer after chilly nights at
OL,11,Ffirst.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
